&nbsp;
Despite this, the President of the PD has been criticised for a part of the internal minority, which considers his opposition to the incisive secretariat. But it is above all the construction of the area and the work of rooting of People's Energy not to satisfy some prominent representatives of the minority. And the fact that it was precisely Bonaccini, as President Pd, to bring the proposal of the name in the direction did not contribute to shaping the souls. In fact: even very close to the president, like Stefano Lepri and Silvia Costa, intervened to stop the proposal immediately.
